    @StyleSheet(value="//cdn.muicss.com/mui-0.9.39/css/mui.min.css") @StyleSheet(value="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.5.0/css/all.css")

 @Viewport(value="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
public class MDDUI
extends com.vaadin.ui.UI
    This UI is the application entry point. A UI may either represent a browser window (or tab) or some part of an HTML page where a Vaadin application is embedded.

    The UI is initialized using init(VaadinRequest). This method is intended to be overridden to add component to the user interface and initialize non-component functionality.
